        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="title">Downloading Update.</h1>
            <hr>
            <p class="subtitle" id="help" style="visibility: hidden">Please download gdreqbot manually: <a href="https://gdreqbot.ddns.net/download">https://gdreqbot.ddns.net/download</p>
